CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season - Making a Point - Albert Thompson (right) of Atlanta, Ga., makes a point during a conversation with Atty. Henry R. Smith and Roland Sawyer at the Frogs' formal. Mr. Thompson is a housing specialist working out of Washington, D.C., with the Housing and Home Finance Agency"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Atty. Henry R. Smith, Roland Sawyer, and Albert Thompson, posed in Gateway Plaza for FROGS formal
